1
00:01:08,359 --> 00:01:09,519
Come on, Your Highness.

2
00:01:32,280 --> 00:01:32,840
Your Highness.

3
00:01:59,200 --> 00:01:59,799
Be careful.

4
00:02:04,120 --> 00:02:05,159
Mother.

5
00:02:05,920 --> 00:02:07,799
Help!

6
00:02:16,919 --> 00:02:18,080
Your Highness.

7
00:02:18,599 --> 00:02:19,120
My dear,

8
00:02:19,680 --> 00:02:21,039
I know I was wrong.

9
00:02:21,479 --> 00:02:23,240
Please don't punish me anymore.

10
00:02:41,319 --> 00:02:42,280
Congratulations, Your Highness.

11
00:02:42,960 --> 00:02:43,599
This time,

12
00:02:44,000 --> 00:02:45,360
you finally took down Prime Minister Shen.

13
00:02:47,599 --> 00:02:48,520
For years,

14
00:02:48,840 --> 00:02:49,599
it was Shen Yi,

15
00:02:49,599 --> 00:02:50,879
this old man, who always stood in the way,

16
00:02:51,599 --> 00:02:53,000
causing my father to have doubts about me,

17
00:02:53,879 --> 00:02:55,240
and delaying my ascension to Crown Prince.

18
00:02:55,840 --> 00:02:57,199
He even wanted to marry his daughter to me.

19
00:02:58,719 --> 00:02:59,439
On the surface,

20
00:02:59,680 --> 00:03:00,680
it was said that with this marriage,

21
00:03:01,639 --> 00:03:03,639
Shen would surely assist me in the future.

22
00:03:04,719 --> 00:03:05,400
But in fact,

23
00:03:06,479 --> 00:03:08,240
he just wants to use him to balance me.

24
00:03:09,080 --> 00:03:10,400
Your Highness, you have endured for many years.

25
00:03:10,759 --> 00:03:11,840
Finally, your wish has come true.

26
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,039
I believe

27
00:03:13,240 --> 00:03:14,120
it won't be long

28
00:03:14,719 --> 00:03:15,800
before I should call you

29
00:03:16,840 --> 00:03:17,680
Crown Prince.

30
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:20,080
You're so clever.

31
00:03:28,280 --> 00:03:29,120
Prince Rui.

32
00:03:33,800 --> 00:03:34,280
What's up?

33
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,280
The palace sent a message.

34
00:03:36,639 --> 00:03:37,520
The imperial edict has been issued.

35
00:03:37,879 --> 00:03:40,000
I've sent someone to the PM's Mansion

36
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:40,879
before the Imperial Guards arrive.

37
00:03:42,000 --> 00:03:42,960
Didn't you say a few days ago

38
00:03:42,960 --> 00:03:44,120
that you missed your father and brother?

39
00:03:45,159 --> 00:03:46,599
Shall I take you home now?

40
00:03:47,400 --> 00:03:48,240
Go home?

41
00:03:48,319 --> 00:03:49,400
Yes, yes.

42
00:03:59,560 --> 00:04:00,439
Mu Jinghao,

43
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,400
my father has served as an official for years

44
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:04,199
and never did anything to harm the country.

45
00:04:04,759 --> 00:04:05,960
He could never have committed treason.

46
00:04:07,120 --> 00:04:09,240
You're the one behind all this.

47
00:04:10,199 --> 00:04:11,159
You made up

48
00:04:11,159 --> 00:04:12,199
this baseless accusation.

49
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,240
So what if I did?

50
00:04:18,240 --> 00:04:18,680
Let him go.

51
00:04:20,000 --> 00:04:20,800
If it weren't for your father

52
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:22,399
being my enemy in the court,

53
00:04:22,879 --> 00:04:25,000
causing my father to suspect me,

54
00:04:25,079 --> 00:04:26,600
and delaying my succession,

55
00:04:27,120 --> 00:04:28,720
I wouldn't have to go to such great lengths.

56
00:04:31,399 --> 00:04:32,759
If your father had said

57
00:04:32,759 --> 00:04:34,279
a good word for me in court,

58
00:04:35,000 --> 00:04:37,800
the entire mansion wouldn't have been implicated.

59
00:04:38,439 --> 00:04:40,040
You frame the loyal,

60
00:04:40,079 --> 00:04:40,920
collude for personal gain,

61
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:41,720
and endanger the court.

62
00:04:42,399 --> 00:04:44,879
How could my father ever align with you?

63
00:04:48,319 --> 00:04:48,720
Your Highness,

64
00:04:49,160 --> 00:04:49,879
Lord Shen has collected

65
00:04:49,879 --> 00:04:51,120
many evidences against you over the years.

66
00:04:51,439 --> 00:04:52,360
Now they've all been destroyed.

67
00:04:57,839 --> 00:04:59,199
You think destroying these

68
00:04:59,959 --> 00:05:01,560
will make His Majesty trust you?

69
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:03,160
You are not fit

70
00:05:03,920 --> 00:05:05,439
to be the Crown Prince!

71
00:05:11,000 --> 00:05:12,120
Whether I am fit or not

72
00:05:12,879 --> 00:05:14,480
is not for a dead man to judge.

73
00:05:16,560 --> 00:05:17,800
The imperial edict hasn't arrived,

74
00:05:18,600 --> 00:05:20,439
yet you want to silence me first.

75
00:05:24,079 --> 00:05:24,680
What about my sister?

76
00:05:25,399 --> 00:05:26,160
What have you done to her?

77
00:05:28,160 --> 00:05:28,759
Brother!

78
00:05:30,959 --> 00:05:31,439
Brother!

79
00:05:32,720 --> 00:05:34,040
Brother!

80
00:05:34,160 --> 00:05:34,600
Brother!

81
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:36,720
I haven't been home in a long time.

82
00:05:37,040 --> 00:05:38,480
I've missed you

83
00:05:39,279 --> 00:05:40,319
and father so much.

84
00:05:41,959 --> 00:05:42,639
Where's father?

85
00:05:42,879 --> 00:05:43,399
Good girl.

86
00:05:44,639 --> 00:05:45,560
Did he bully you?

87
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:49,040
By the way,

88
00:05:49,800 --> 00:05:50,759
the PM's Residence was attacked,

89
00:05:51,600 --> 00:05:52,480
your sister

90
00:05:52,759 --> 00:05:53,600
also played a role.

91
00:05:54,319 --> 00:05:56,399
Though she's like a child,

92
00:05:57,040 --> 00:05:58,240
but as the saying goes,

93
00:05:59,319 --> 00:06:00,800
children tell the truth.

94
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,959
Justice will be done.

95
00:06:08,480 --> 00:06:09,240
Mu Jinghao,

96
00:06:10,000 --> 00:06:11,759
you will eventually reap what you sow.

97
00:06:11,759 --> 00:06:13,160
Shen Tong colluded with the enemy,

98
00:06:13,560 --> 00:06:15,439
and his family tried to escape.

99
00:06:15,879 --> 00:06:17,240
After being caught by me,

100
00:06:17,480 --> 00:06:19,000
they confessed and were executed.

101
00:06:23,959 --> 00:06:24,399
Brother.

102
00:06:25,199 --> 00:06:25,600
Brother.

103
00:06:25,920 --> 00:06:27,160
I'm so scared.

104
00:06:27,160 --> 00:06:28,199
What's going on?

105
00:06:28,199 --> 00:06:28,920
Don't be afraid.

106
00:06:29,240 --> 00:06:29,639
I'm here.

107
00:06:30,759 --> 00:06:31,079
Brother.

108
00:06:54,120 --> 00:06:54,639
Brother.

109
00:06:56,480 --> 00:06:57,160
Brother.

110
00:06:57,680 --> 00:06:59,279
Brother, where are you?

111
00:06:59,319 --> 00:07:01,360
I'm so scared, brother.

112
00:07:02,040 --> 00:07:04,160
The imperial edict has arrived.

113
00:07:07,519 --> 00:07:10,040
By the mandate of heaven, the Emperor hereby decrees.

114
00:07:10,800 --> 00:07:12,839
Princess Consort of Rui has lost her mind,

115
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:15,879
and has no connection with the case of Lord Shen.

116
00:07:16,240 --> 00:07:16,600
Brother.

117
00:07:16,600 --> 00:07:18,920
Her death penalty is exempted,

118
00:07:19,160 --> 00:07:20,600
but she can't escape from the living penalty.

119
00:07:20,800 --> 00:07:21,240
Brother.

120
00:07:21,240 --> 00:07:23,439
She is hereby ordered to move out of the mansion,

121
00:07:23,959 --> 00:07:26,399
and enter Lingguo Temple for cultivation.

122
00:07:26,759 --> 00:07:27,480
[without permission,]

123
00:07:27,800 --> 00:07:29,839
[she is not allowed to leave.]

124
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,600
[As decreed by the Emperor.]

125
00:07:31,600 --> 00:07:34,279
Brother, where are you?

126
00:07:39,680 --> 00:07:40,120
Let's go.

127
00:07:45,959 --> 00:07:46,639
Brother.

128
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,639
Brother, where are you?

129
00:07:49,639 --> 00:07:51,279
Brother, I'm scared.

130
00:07:51,360 --> 00:07:54,439
Brother, brother.

131
00:08:15,360 --> 00:08:16,519
Where are we going?

132
00:08:16,879 --> 00:08:18,360
Where are my brother and father?

133
00:08:19,040 --> 00:08:19,720
Master Wu Xin,

134
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:22,240
she's the daughter of the Prime Minister.

135
00:08:23,360 --> 00:08:25,240
Wasn't the whole family executed?

136
00:08:25,759 --> 00:08:27,439
Why was she sent to Lingguo Temple?

137
00:08:27,759 --> 00:08:28,800
Will she bring any trouble

138
00:08:28,879 --> 00:08:29,920
to the temple in the future?

139
00:08:31,319 --> 00:08:31,600
Go,

140
00:08:32,000 --> 00:08:33,279
find a remote place for her.

141
00:08:33,600 --> 00:08:34,799
To avoid causing us trouble.

142
00:08:34,840 --> 00:08:35,320
Yes.

143
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:38,519
Your Highness,

144
00:08:39,000 --> 00:08:40,559
just arrange her in my courtyard.

145
00:08:40,799 --> 00:08:41,679
You may go now.

146
00:08:42,840 --> 00:08:43,320
Yes.

147
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:43,759
Yes.

148
00:08:52,399 --> 00:08:53,399
Poor child,

149
00:08:54,559 --> 00:08:55,600
you've suffered too much.

150
00:08:58,519 --> 00:08:59,480
Mother.

151
00:09:03,159 --> 00:09:04,279
Silly girl.

152
00:09:04,759 --> 00:09:07,120
Mother, why did you come so late?

153
00:09:19,279 --> 00:09:20,519
She's been here for over half a month.

154
00:09:21,639 --> 00:09:23,200
When will she recover her mind?

155
00:09:24,600 --> 00:09:25,840
I'm afraid her madness

156
00:09:26,240 --> 00:09:27,480
is not an accident.

157
00:09:27,759 --> 00:09:29,200
I've checked her pulse.

158
00:09:29,440 --> 00:09:30,480
It's a sign of poisoning.

159
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:32,840
Plus the repeated shocks,

160
00:09:33,360 --> 00:09:34,759
she may never recover.

161
00:09:36,240 --> 00:09:37,399
Is there no other way?

162
00:09:38,559 --> 00:09:39,879
Maybe forgetting everything

163
00:09:40,879 --> 00:09:42,240
is the best choice

164
00:09:42,240 --> 00:09:43,799
to forget everything.

165
00:09:44,879 --> 00:09:46,840
Mom, mom.

166
00:09:47,360 --> 00:09:49,279
I'm here.

167
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:51,720
I'm here.

168
00:09:51,840 --> 00:09:52,879
Mom, I...

169
00:09:53,840 --> 00:09:54,919
Don't be afraid.

170
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:58,279
I'm here.

171
00:09:58,840 --> 00:09:59,279
Don't be afraid.

172
00:10:03,879 --> 00:10:04,639
Sui'er, don't be afraid.

173
00:10:05,159 --> 00:10:07,240
This big brother is here to protect us.

174
00:10:07,519 --> 00:10:08,320
He's not a bad person.

175
00:10:12,399 --> 00:10:13,200
Brother,

176
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:17,200
protect us.

177
00:10:20,679 --> 00:10:22,279
I like you.

178
00:10:29,480 --> 00:10:30,279
You like...

179
00:10:32,039 --> 00:10:33,240
I like this.

180
00:10:40,440 --> 00:10:40,919
Then it's yours.

181
00:10:48,480 --> 00:10:49,240
Your Highness,

182
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:51,720
the whole family has been killed.

183
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:54,320
When will His Majesty agree to divorce?

184
00:10:54,759 --> 00:10:55,720
When will I

185
00:10:55,720 --> 00:10:57,279
become the principal consort?

186
00:10:57,679 --> 00:10:58,440
Just wait a little longer.

187
00:10:59,240 --> 00:11:00,960
Without the support of the PM's Mansion,

188
00:11:01,799 --> 00:11:03,240
it's easy for me to deal with her.

189
00:11:03,399 --> 00:11:04,759
At that time,

190
00:11:05,159 --> 00:11:06,919
can my father still want a dead woman to be his daughter-in-law?

191
00:11:08,399 --> 00:11:09,559
But I heard that

192
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:11,440
she seems to have sought the protection

193
00:11:11,559 --> 00:11:13,320
of Consort Dowager Li in Lingguo Temple.

194
00:11:13,519 --> 00:11:15,159
She's just a former consort.

195
00:11:15,879 --> 00:11:16,960
How long can she protect her?

196
00:11:17,919 --> 00:11:18,440
Don't worry.

197
00:11:19,240 --> 00:11:20,120
The position of principal consort

198
00:11:20,960 --> 00:11:21,759
will be yours sooner or later.

199
00:11:29,879 --> 00:11:30,480
Sui'er.

200
00:11:30,840 --> 00:11:31,440
Mother.

201
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:33,200
Sui'er,

202
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:35,480
let's play hide and seek,

203
00:11:35,480 --> 00:11:36,200
shall we?

204
00:11:36,720 --> 00:11:37,639
Hide and seek?

205
00:11:37,960 --> 00:11:38,840
Yes.

206
00:11:38,840 --> 00:11:39,240
Come on.

207
00:11:47,919 --> 00:11:48,480
Sui'er,

208
00:11:48,960 --> 00:11:50,200
Stay here.

209
00:11:50,720 --> 00:11:51,440
Don't make a sound,

210
00:11:51,759 --> 00:11:52,639
and don't talk.

211
00:11:53,559 --> 00:11:54,720
Okay, don't talk.

212
00:11:56,440 --> 00:11:56,879
And,

213
00:11:57,559 --> 00:11:58,039
Sui'er,

214
00:11:58,759 --> 00:11:59,799
if I don't come to you

215
00:12:00,360 --> 00:12:02,000
by tomorrow morning,

216
00:12:02,480 --> 00:12:03,840
take this jade pendant

217
00:12:04,240 --> 00:12:06,799
and find the big brother who protects us.

218
00:12:07,039 --> 00:12:07,720
I've met him.

219
00:12:08,120 --> 00:12:09,639
He also gave me a jade pendant.

220
00:12:14,399 --> 00:12:15,000
Sui'er,

221
00:12:17,600 --> 00:12:18,039
stay here.

222
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:19,240
Don't talk,

223
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:20,759
and don't peek.
